comments: Hayes (NOP) is moving alongside Okoro's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together at the same spot.
Osman (CLE) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and he slides his pivot foot on the perimeter.
Hart (NOP) brushes Love's (CLE) off arm and marginal contact occurs during the shot near the rim.
Love (CLE) places his left hand on Hart's (NOP) shoulder and restricts Hart's ability to secure the rebound.

As Hart (NOP) reaches for the rebound his arm makes some contact with Love's (CLE) head.   Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Valanciunas (NOP) makes contact with the ball and with the part of Love's (CLE) hand that is on the ball during rebounding.

Hayes (NOP) contests Allen's (CLE) shot near the rim and marginal contact occurs with the top of Allen's head. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Goodwin (CLE) does not step out of bounds and he legally saves the ball.
Hart (NOP) and Love (CLE) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Hayes (NOP) extends his hands into Okoro's (CLE) path and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Stevens (CLE) brings his arm forward towards Hart (NOP) and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Valanciunas (NOP) is already in Stevens' (CLE) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Stevens (CLE) is moving alongside Graham's (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs as Graham elevates for his shot.

As Stevens (CLE) reaches for the rebound, marginal contact occurs with Valanciunas' (NOP) head.  Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) attempts to commit a take foul on Goodwin (CLE), and the contact is marginal.
Clark (NOP) clamps and holds Love's (CLE) arm, restricting his ability to secure the rebound.
Allen (CLE) is moving alongside Valanciunas' (NOP) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Hart (NOP) commits a take foul on Stevens (CLE).
